Dialogue: 0,0:23:36.23,0:23:39.23,Default,Pencilgon,0,0,0,,They live for a moment, \Nthen remain for eternity...
Dialogue: 0,0:23:39.90,0:23:42.11,Default,Pencilgon,0,0,0,,The flower's name reflects \Nthat— "Setsunatowa."
Dialogue: 0,0:23:42.44,0:23:44.24,Default,Pencilgon,0,0,0,,Perfect for you and me, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:23:47.28,0:23:52.20,Default,Pencilgon,0,0,0,,Boy, but it wasn't easy to get these.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:52.20,0:23:56.00,Default,Pencilgon,0,0,0,,All my equipment got \Nconfiscated when I respawned.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:05.13,0:24:07.76,Flashback,Pencilgon,0,0,0,,Sorry, but I'm in a hurry.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:07.76,0:24:11.22,Flashback,Pencilgon,0,0,0,,You mind taking me on the \Nsecret route to Thirdrema?
Dialogue: 0,0:24:12.10,0:24:14.02,Flashback,Mob,0,0,0,,So, where's my payment?
Dialogue: 0,0:24:14.02,0:24:15.14,Flashback,Pencilgon,0,0,0,,Hey, thanks!
Dialogue: 0,0:24:15.14,0:24:16.81,Flashback,Pencilgon,0,0,0,,I'll take it on loan, if you don't mind.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:16.81,0:24:18.94,Flashback,Pencilgon,0,0,0,,I'm in a hurry, so later!
Dialogue: 0,0:24:20.65,0:24:22.73,Flashback,NPC Flower Seller,0,0,0,,Thank you for saving me.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:23.23,0:24:25.94,Flashback,NPC Flower Seller,0,0,0,,Please take this, as an \Nexpression of my gratitude.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:28.36,0:24:31.28,Flashback,Pencilgon,0,0,0,,I cleared the event and got the loot!
Dialogue: 0,0:24:36.66,0:24:37.37,Flashback,Guard,0,0,0,,Hey!
Dialogue: 0,0:24:41.38,0:24:45.30,Default,Pencilgon,0,0,0,,I knew you would be gone.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:46.21,0:24:49.76,Default,Pencilgon,0,0,0,,But I wanted to make it here before dawn.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:50.59,0:24:52.76,Default,Pencilgon,0,0,0,,Just in case... you know?
Dialogue: 0,0:24:54.43,0:24:57.77,Default,Pencilgon,0,0,0,,Kind of a silly thing to hope for, I know.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:59.48,0:25:02.81,Default,Pencilgon,0,0,0,,Boy, am I sentimental or what?
Dialogue: 0,0:25:04.90,0:25:06.82,Default,Pencilgon,0,0,0,,Well, I'll be back.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:07.40,0:25:08.32,Default,Pencilgon,0,0,0,,Set-chan.
